劾下台的總統。當局將於60日內舉行大選。<br />\n<br />\n消息公布後，韓圜短線走強，兌美元及港元現升約0.2%。目前港元兌韓圜現報148.8098，美元兌韓圜則報1155.64。<br />\n<br />\n去年12月9日，韓國國會234名議員投票通過彈劾朴槿惠，相隔91日後，憲法法院終於作出最終裁決，較2004年前總統盧武鉉遭彈劾時的63日長。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，此次彈劾判決有5個爭論焦點，包括崔順實干政、濫用總統職權、「世越號」沉船事件發生當天朴槿惠「消失7小時」的疑惑、施壓更換媒體總裁、與閨密崔順實共謀，以及強迫大集團捐款。"},{"pid":"ee7844dd98527a9fefcc07bb094f73a5b97e64a2","tid":150318,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:04:36.000Z","msg":"掉佢雞蛋就岩啦"},{"pid":"62e3421d5ae3e0a62bc3c9354fbe96fd891cbc3c","tid":150318,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"睇下女人都撞撚哂車"},{"pid":"68ebea7897c5206537d2311b693eaac12196670f","tid":150318,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"女人根本就唔適合做特首"},{"pid":"b6f7469016f6184a3b84a0574588e18289b558f4","tid":150318,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02b06844db2fb60c35659923546275d58708c0e","tid":150318,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b641b31c870d5c47982221b5a7e4aee11a1a81","tid":150318,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"支那真係癌細胞邊個近佢衰邊個"},{"pid":"05424748111288144da2cfd88929c0149db06b6e","tid":150318,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:18:09.000Z","msg":"早就應該落台,俾邪教影響治國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2d11d92c7b26018e9df519b066d84b6145b9f5","tid":150318,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a25425e5b8aa058da91dbfdf7be47ad0050f24","tid":150318,"uid":6